Reasoning: The paper discusses the challenges of controlling software and system development projects, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The paper also discusses the architecture and implementation of a software project control center, which involves programming languages (cs.PL) and software design (cs.SD). The paper also mentions the need for sustainability and appropriate tool support, which could fall under cybernetics (cs.CY) and computer engineering (cs.CE).
